723574f-a.folder: Trinity Place & Thames Street, Manhattan, NY
723574f-a.text:
90-88, 86-78 and (part of) 76-70 Trinity Place, at, adjoining and south of the S.W. corner of Thames Street (right, not shown), showing consecutively, the New York University School of Commerce (Wall Street divisions), the New York Curb Exchange and Trinity Court building. Subsequent to 1921.
Ewing Galloway.
